data.description: LSituated on a large corner lot in the Michaux Creek subdivision in Midlothian! Easy access to 288, Powhite, Westchester Commons, shopping, dining, hospitals and health facilites. Blue Ribbon Chesterfield Schools! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, vinyl sided home boasts spacious eat-in kitchen with hardwoods, center island, recessed lighting pantry, breakfast nook with vaulted ceiling and conveniently located utility/laundry room tucked away around corner providing access to 1-car front entry garage. Formal living room w/ hardwoods, chandelier, crown & chair molding. Spacious family room with gas fireplace, bay window, recessed lighting, sliding glass doors to rear 18x10 deck and rear staircase. The master suite has a large walk-in closet with a master bath that includes a garden tub and shower. Roof Replaced in 2018. Fully fenced in rear yard
